/* STDLIB/iii/omnia/gnosis.iii -- GNOSIS (the KNOWING): software IS the
 * physics the summit proved -- the bridge that turns the capstone axioms
 * onto code itself.
 *
 * THE KEYSTONE: the CPU has been a p-adic engine all along.  u64 arithmetic
 * IS Z_2 truncated to 64 digits -- wrapping is the truncation ideal, the
 * carry chain is the 2-adic grid law.  Arm 290 WITNESSES the identity: the
 * native ALU against the klisi digit engine at KP=2, two engines one ring,
 * including the wrap 0xFFFF..F + 1 = 0 on both sides.  Everything after
 * rides that identity:
 *
 *   THE ORBIT ORACLE (arms 291-292, Theorem I weaponized): halting for the
 *   affine/linear loop fragment over the machine's own rings, DECIDED by
 *   valuation -- never simulated to infinity.
 *     - `while x != 0 { x += c }` on w-bit words halts iff v_2(c) <= v_2(x0)
 *       (0 lies on the orbit iff x0 is in the subgroup <c> iff
 *       gcd(c, 2^w) | x0).  The decision rule is verified by COMPLETE
 *       ENUMERATION of the small ring -- ALL 65536 (c, x0) pairs of Z/2^8,
 *       each orbit run to its group-order bound, zero disagreements -- and
 *       the THEOREM carries it to Z/2^64, where a single orbit can exceed
 *       2^60 steps and simulation is impossible: decided instances are
 *       cross-checked by short exact runs (halting side) and by the
 *       subgroup obstruction x0 mod 2^(v2 c) != 0 (diverging side);
 *     - `x <<= 1` halts in <= w steps (valuation grows every step: the
 *       archimedean loop bound IS a 2-adic statement);
 *     - an INVERTIBLE linear map (xorshift -- the reversible organ's own
 *       law) NEVER reaches 0 from x0 != 0: bijectivity fixes 0, so
 *       nontermination is PROVEN, not timed out -- the complete permutation
 *       table of the 8-bit variant is saturated and the orbit closed.
 *
 *   THE INTERLEAVING ORBIT (arms 293-294, Theorem II weaponized): threads
 *   are the boolean-refutation arm turned onto schedules.
 *     - PETERSON's lock: the FULL reachable state space saturated (BFS to
 *       closure, the SYMMETRIA pattern); mutual exclusion holds in EVERY
 *       reachable state and no reachable state is stuck -- safety as
 *       saturation, not testing.  The negative control: the check-then-set
 *       protocol (TOCTOU) reaches both-in-critical-section -- the race
 *       WITNESSED exactly;
 *     - the STORE-BUFFERING litmus: all sequentially-consistent
 *       interleavings enumerated (the complete orbit of schedules);
 *       outcome (0,0) is UNREACHABLE under SC -- the classical bound --
 *       and REACHED the moment store-load reordering is admitted: the
 *       exact boundary of boolean causality in memory models, the CHSH
 *       shape on silicon;
 *
 *   THE VERDICT LOOP (arm 295, the autopoietic seat): the organism meters
 *   ITS OWN engines.  riza's two gcd engines run the same workload under
 *   the exact op-meter; the measured winner must BE the dispatcher's
 *   default -- if the substrate ever drifts, this arm reddens and demands
 *   a new verdict.  Self-optimization as a standing proof obligation, on
 *   the DETERMINISTIC meter (op-count is the machine's invariant energy;
 *   wall time is weather);
 *
 *   THE EXACT ARGMIN (arm 296, the analytic optimizer): minimize the
 *   summit's own separation quartic on [0,2] with a CERTIFICATE: P'' has
 *   no real root and is positive (P' strictly increasing), P' has exactly
 *   one root (Sturm), the minimum value 0 sits at t=1, and GLOBAL
 *   nonnegativity is certified by the node factorization P = g^2 u with
 *   u > 0 -- the sum-of-squares witness the singularity analysis already
 *   minted.  No descent, no epsilon: the true bottom of the hill, proven;
 *
 *   THE SCROLL (arm 297): the derived facts sealed by EIDOLOS with a
 *   deterministic canonical address, entailing consequences absent from
 *   the text and refusing their reversals.
 *
 *   THE CHRONOMETER (arm 298, the oracle made QUANTITATIVE): the orbit
 *   oracle decides WHETHER; the inverse faculty (klisi kd_inv/kl_inv2_u64,
 *   Hensel/Newton) mints WHEN -- the exact first-arrival count
 *   n = ((0-x0)>>v) inv(c>>v) mod 2^(64-v), verified by COMPLETE
 *   enumeration of Z/2^8 (every halting pair, simulated arrival == closed
 *   form, zero disagreements; uniqueness mod 2^(8-v) makes it THE first
 *   arrival) and carried by the theorem to Z/2^64, where an orbit beyond
 *   2^60 steps has its arrival computed O(1) and CONFIRMED by the
 *   substrate identity in one mul+add -- and HOW MUCH: the total work
 *   n x0 + c n(n-1)/2 in exact Q, cross-sworn to MERIS's independent
 *   Stirling power-sum engine (cross-organ, two engines one integer);
 *
 *   THE DIVISION BRIDGE (arm 299): division rides the substrate identity
 *   -- exact division IS multiplication by the Hensel inverse (native and
 *   digit engines, one law); the LIVE planner seg_div_plan (the organ
 *   cg_r3 consults) driven over a divisor battery with the GM bound
 *   re-derived and the mulhi route checked against the ALU divider (two
 *   engines, one quotient); and the Montgomery kernel n' = -inv(n) with
 *   n n' == -1 minted from the same faculty.
 *
 * Truth is a CONDITION OF MOTION: gn_selfprove (arms 290..299).  NO gate
 * of its own (the summit gate compiles and drives this organ).
 * NIH: composes klisi (the ring + the inverse), meris (the power-sum
 * engine), riza+pyrgos (the exact engines), ser_egraph (the live division
 * planner), eidolos (the scroll).  Software is not TRANSLATED into physics;
 * it is RECOGNIZED as physics.  Ring R-1. */
module omnia_gnosis

